{SOUTH has 20 points, a pretty strong hand to open 1\H. 

NORTH has 12 points, and makes a Limit Raise, a jump to 3\H.

SOUTH is very, very close to bidding a slam. But she knows NORTH has 12 points at most, so she should 
take the safe position and just bid 4\H.}

